NetScaler is a line of networking products owned by Citrix Systems. The products consist of NetScaler ADC, an application delivery controller (ADC), NetScaler AppFirewall, an application firewall, NetScaler Unified Gateway, NetScaler Management & Analytics System, and NetScaler SD-WAN, which provides software-defined wide-area networking management. NetScaler was initially developed in 1999 and acquired by Citrix in 2005. Citrix consolidated all of its networking products under the NetScaler brand in 2016.
